snippet.title: Kickerinho - September Update Teaser  [iOS/Android/WP8]
snippet.description:
JUST *TAP* *TAP* AND KEEP IT UP!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kickerinho

Apple AppStore: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id895557340

Google Play https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tabascointeractive.kickerinho

Amazon http://www.amazon.com/Tabasco-Interactive-Kickerinho/dp/B00M70ITRM

http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/kickerinho/991d10f9-8f5d-4240-af53-176dda71488e

Tap tap and keep it up!

Kickerinho 1.1 arrives and in it you will find:

* Unlock the ultimate, breath taking, flame spitting award:  the Fire Ball!
* Total 11 new awards and achievements
* Long awaited in app purchase that removes the ads.
* New menu in which you can select the ball you love the most!
